title: I Started A Joke
lyrics: / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / X2 I started a joke Which started the whole world  crying But I didn't  see That the joke was on me, oh no (1, 4: C Em F G ; 2, 3: C) I looked at the skies Running my hands over my eyes And I fell out of bed Hurting my head From things that I'd said That the joke was on  me   Oh...
